<li><small>Matthews, Peter. (1991). <i>Morphology</i> (2nd ed.). Cambridge: Cambridge University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521410436" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-41043-6</a> (hb); <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521422566" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-42256-6</a> (pbk).</small></li>
